{
  "name": "RPlog_35_ISY_Competition_Banger_vs_Black_Butterfly",
  "title": "Banger vs. Black Butterfly",
  "summary": "In the 35 ISY Imperial fighter-simulator championship, Marshal Krieg Inrokana, flying under the call sign Banger, faces the young pilot Sarai, the Black Butterfly, in his final regular-season match. Krieg opens aggressively, trash-talking matched by hard flying, but Sarai proves maddeningly elusive, slipping out of volley after volley with barrel rolls and frantic dives even as her shields are stripped away. Round after round Krieg lands hits while Sarai struggles to score in return, her evasive bomber-trained instincts frustrating his attempts at a clean kill. Eventually a pair of solid hits locks down her consoles and ends the duel in Banger's favor, closing out his run through the championship's regular matches. Krieg comes away impressed by the Butterfly's defensive skill.",
